          <div class="content">
            <h2 class="is-bold has-text-centered">Keep Your Assets</h2>
            <p>
              Your domains are important assets. You won't have to worry about
              losing them while renting them out. Cancel your listing when you
              need to.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="control has-addons has-addons-centered margin-top-50">
        <a class="button is-accent is-large" href="/sellers" title="Benefits of listing on DomaHub">
